	<h1 class="page-header">One last thing about big fans...</h1>
    
    <div class="grid onehalf">
    	<p>Building a tight group of your most dedicated fans is more important than ever. Having 100,000 Facebook Fans or Twitter Followers is great, but it doesn't necessarily translate into you making a living from your craft.</p>
		<p>On the flip side, having a group of just <strong>1,000 "true fans"</strong> who are willing support you with $10/month works out to <strong>$120,000/year</strong>. True fans are very powerful.</p>
		<p>Check out this blog post called <a href="http://www.kk.org/thetechnium/archives/2008/03/1000_true_fans.php" target="_blank">1,000 True Fans</a> to dive deeper.</p>
    </div>
